              A measured, repeatable result across real projects.
            </p>
            <div class="proof-tag-row">
              <span class="proof-tag">Productivity</span>
              <span class="proof-tag">Workflow Design</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="proof-card reveal">
            <div class="proof-number">02</div>
            <h3 class="proof-title">WhatsApp Business Automation</h3>
            <p class="proof-body">
              Built an AI-powered WhatsApp bot handling scheduling, quoting, and
              customer enquiries. Fully automated, running 24/7, reducing response
              time from hours to seconds.
            </p>
            <div class="proof-tag-row">
              <span class="proof-tag">Chatbot</span>
              <span class="proof-tag">Customer Service</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="proof-card reveal">
            <div class="proof-number">03</div>
            <h3 class="proof-title">Two Solo Developers → Market</h3>
            <p class="proof-body">
              Two solo developers used our AI-augmented workflows to take products
              from concept to launch. One built and shipped a complete product
              end-to-end. Another, a non-technical founder, built and sold an
              app for £20k in under 12 months. No teams. No agencies.
            </p>
            <div class="proof-tag-row">
              <span class="proof-tag">Solo Developers</span>
              <span class="proof-tag">Go-to-Market</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ===== FAQ ===== -->
    <section class="faq" id="faq">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header reveal">
          <p class="section-tag">Common questions</p>
          <h2 class="section-title">Frequently asked questions about AI consultancy</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-list">
